Purpose
=======

This is a simple, Sinatra based web-based tool to explore and deliver the data in wb_sms_water.sqlite. 
Lumin is a team based out of the Integrated Product Design (IPD) program at the University of Pennsylvania.

Setup
=========

Download. (This data was downloaded from the government's website at http://72.26.224.173/water/Default.aspx, saved as an Excel file, then as an CSV file and imported into the sqlite file via `ruby csv_to_sql.rb wb_sms_water.csv wb_sms_water`.)
Run with `ruby stats.rb.`

